metadata.name: 4 Divas
metadata.description: AI Creation by H.Magnus, 2021. Using VQGan + CLIP in two stages, processing two different images over a given text. Both files are later processed into Unreal Engine, and this is the result. HQ resolution. The artwork intend to express the female magical powers and the spots, their resolution and standing upon society. The blank space come to represent their endless possibilities, once they get released themselves of old prejudices and chains
